      <h1 class='title'>The Financing of Terrorism in Northern Ireland</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='westminster-hall-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 01 May 2003 vol 404 cc143-4WH</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_143wh' title='Col. 143WH &mdash; HC Deb 01 May 2003 vol 404 c143WH' name='column_143wh' href='#column_143wh' rel='bookmark'>143WH</a>
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_2' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">[Relevant documents: Fourth Report from the Northern Ireland Affairs Committee, Session 2001&#x2013;02, HC 978-I, and the Government's response thereto, Sixth Special Report, Session 2001&#x2013;02, HC 1347.]</span>
      </p>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_144wh' title='Col. 144WH &mdash; HC Deb 01 May 2003 vol 404 c144WH' name='column_144wh' href='#column_144wh' rel='bookmark'>144WH</a>
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_3' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Motion made, and Question proposed,</span> That the sitting be now adjourned.&#x2014;<span class="italic">[Derek Twigg.]</span>
      </p>
      
      <span class='time published'><a href="#2003-05-01T14:30:00Z" name="2003-05-01T14:30:00Z"><abbr class="dtstart" title="2003-05-01T14:30:00Z">2.30 pm</abbr></a></span>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_5'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-michael-mates' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_5' title='Link to this speech by Mr Michael Mates' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-michael-mates" title="Mr Michael Mates">Mr. Michael Mates</a></cite>
          <span class='member_constituency'><a href="/constituencies/hampshire-east" title="Hampshire East">(East Hampshire)</a></span>
          <p class='first-para'>
            I am happy to agree to this adjournment in the special circumstances that we are needed elsewhere. I shall raise a point of order in the Chamber after questions to try to ensure that we have a system that does not put us all in the position of having to adjourn a debate that could more easily be postponed until the important statement is over. In the circumstances, I am happy to agree with the Government's motion.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_6' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Question put and agreed to.</span>
      </p>
      
      <p class='procedural'>
        <a class='permalink' href='#S6CV0404P0_20030501_WH_7' title='Link to this contribution' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
        <span class="italic">Adjourned accordingly at half-past Two o'clock.</span>
      </p>
